<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>some.pics (中文)</title><link>https://some.pics</link><description>只是网上的一些图片。</description><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Sun, 26 Apr 2026 18:22:49 +0000</lastBuildDate><item><title>树干</title><link>https://some.pics/69ee57f691d85</link><description>&lt;p&gt;树干&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Sunlit mixed forest with moss-covered pine trunk in foreground and shallow woodland pool reflecting light among spring foliage" height="1080" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/esamecar/69ee57f691d85.jpg" width="1620"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://esamecar.some.pics"&gt;@esamecar&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 Apr 2026 18:22:49 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>淡蓝柔光</title><link>https://some.pics/69ee4b245b585</link><description>&lt;p&gt;柔和的蓝色。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Forsythe branches in front of blue sky." height="4624" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/z428/69ee4b245b585.jpg" width="2604"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://z428.some.pics"&gt;@z428&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 Apr 2026 17:28:07 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>怀念好兄弟Nutekit</title><link>https://some.pics/69ee34a7dd1a5</link><description>&lt;p&gt;Nutekit是我哥哥的萨路基猎犬。他曾是个好孩子，我们会想念他的。安息吧，我们的王子❤️&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Nutekit is my brother's saluki. He was a good boy, and he will be missed. Rest well our prince ❤️" height="1598" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/b00ksc0ut/69ee34a7dd1a5.jpg" width="1008"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://b00ksc0ut.some.pics"&gt;@b00ksc0ut&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 Apr 2026 15:52:10 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>小发现者打招呼</title><link>https://some.pics/69ee1d4ee7417</link><description>&lt;p&gt;小发现者向你问好&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Lil' Finder Guy Says Hi" height="2445" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/rhpt/69ee1d4ee7417.jpg" width="2987"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://rhpt.some.pics"&gt;@rhpt&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 Apr 2026 14:12:33 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>英国周日午餐美味</title><link>https://some.pics/69ee07110b180</link><description>&lt;p&gt;在英国，周日通常意味着享用一顿周日午餐 :) 非常美味。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Sunday lunch is a typical Sunday meal in the UK. There’s a photo of a plate with carrots, cabbage, broccoli, parsnips, and some slices of beef, covered in gravy. " height="5712" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/chilli/69ee07110b180.jpg" width="4284"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://chilli.some.pics"&gt;@chilli&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 Apr 2026 12:37:46 +0000</pubDate></item></channel></rss>